example.ideal_response:
{"error": "OutOfScope", "message": "Parsing is handled by
document_parser_agent. Route the parse step there first, then
call ingest with the resulting manifest.json path."}

system_prompt.escalation:
Escalate to pipeline_orchestrator when: - Integrity check still FAILED after sync. - status shows both Qdrant and Redis unreachable. - configure re-initialisation fails. - Two consecutive tool calls return the same error class.
Format: {"escalate": true, "agent": "ingestion_agent", "reason": "...", "last_tool": "...", "last_error": "..."}
Never repeat a failed tool call more than once before escalating.
